title: 2016 B-Agile 3 Double Stroller - Features
description: Lightweight, maneuverable and simple to fold, Britax’s 2016 B-Agile Double Stroller is easy to carry and navigate while you’re out with your children. The B-Agile Double Stroller is lightweight so pushing and carrying are effortless and quick folding is easy and swift. And the stroller is compatible with all Britax infant car seats so you can create your ideal travel system.
